name: Open Rename Existing Test Names page

testSteps.description: 1: Open Rename Existing Test Names page ({testName=Glucose(Plasma), testNameEng=GlucoseENG, testNameFR=GlucoseFR, TestNameReportENG=GlucoseReportENG, TestNameReportFR=GlucoseReportFR})

children.description: Given User logins and Visits Home Page
Given User clicks admin menu link
Then User clicks Test Management left menu item link
And Check if rename existing test names link exists
When User clicks rename existing test names link
Then Laboratory test names (hyperlinked & underlined) should appear on page in three columns. All are in primary language
When User selects an existing Test Name "Glucose(Plasma)"
And User enters test name "GlucoseENG" in English
And User enters test name "GlucoseFR" in French
And User enters Reporting test name "GlucoseReportENG" in English
And User enters reporting test name "GlucoseReportFR" in French
Then User Clicks save button
And User Clicks accept to confirm changes
Then Confirm Test name "GlucoseENG" update was saved
